{"repo": "InternLM/xtuner", "pull_number": 1624, "instance_id": "InternLM__xtuner-1624", "issue_numbers": [1623], "base_commit": "fb28789f5827c3cf0c113c1584b6d155c8c79b27", "patch": "diff --git a/xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py b/xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py\nindex 71406c55d..77f5f7283 100644\n--- a/xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py\n+++ b/xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py\n@@ -349,6 +349,11 @@ def _transform_rollout_config_to_server_configs(self) -> Namespace:\n                     {\n                         \"LMDEPLOY_DP_MASTER_ADDR\": dist_addr,\n                         \"LMDEPLOY_DP_MASTER_PORT\": dist_port,\n+                        # DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK is required by DLBlas's DeepEP\n+                        # token dispatcher used in lmdeploy EP mode. Without it,\n+                        # lmdeploy will fail during warmup.\n+                        # Ref: https://github.com/DeepLink-org/DLBlas/blob/aae23445/dlblas/layers/moe/token_dispatcher.py#L81\n+                        # Ref: https://github.com/InternLM/lmdeploy/blob/81627e3d/lmdeploy/utils.py#L375\n                         \"DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK\": str(max_batch_size),\n                     }\n                 )\n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "[Docs] add comment on special  env `DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK`\n\n", "hints_text": "@claude make a PR to add comment at https://github.com/InternLM/xtuner/blob/fb28789f5827c3cf0c113c1584b6d155c8c79b27/xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py#L352 . Please note that this env `DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK` is introduced in `https://github.com/DeepLink-org/DLBlas/blob/aae234451e772339f4fd075e00894205b87024fc/dlblas/layers/moe/token_dispatcher.py#L81` and dlbas is used by lmdeploy ep mode, without this env settings, lmdeploy would fail at warmup (https://github.com/InternLM/lmdeploy/blob/81627e3dea6ce6691b078cc3e0be03e9a64122fb/lmdeploy/utils.py#L375).\n\n", "all_hints_text": "@claude make a PR to add comment at https://github.com/InternLM/xtuner/blob/fb28789f5827c3cf0c113c1584b6d155c8c79b27/xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py#L352 . Please note that this env `DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK` is introduced in `https://github.com/DeepLink-org/DLBlas/blob/aae234451e772339f4fd075e00894205b87024fc/dlblas/layers/moe/token_dispatcher.py#L81` and dlbas is used by lmdeploy ep mode, without this env settings, lmdeploy would fail at warmup (https://github.com/InternLM/lmdeploy/blob/81627e3dea6ce6691b078cc3e0be03e9a64122fb/lmdeploy/utils.py#L375).\n**Claude:** Added a comment explaining the `DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK` environment variable at `xtuner/v1/ray/rollout/lmdeploy.py:352`, as requested.\n\n**Actions taken:**\n- Added an inline comment explaining that `DEEPEP_MAX_TOKENS_PER_RANK` is required by DLBlas's DeepEP token dispatcher in lmdeploy EP mode, and that without it lmdeploy fails during warmup.\n- Included references to the relevant DLBlas and lmdeploy source lines.\n- Created PR: https://github.com/InternLM/xtuner/pull/1624 (commit https://github.com/InternLM/xtuner/commit/b381d67)\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/InternLM/xtuner/commit/b381d67266cb545c9ce3a6f2b804cf7f32b97bf4"], "created_at": "2026-03-24T10:32:12Z"}
